== Weapon System Heatmap

#figure(
  image("report_05_weapon_heatmap.png", width: 100%),
  caption: [Individual weapon system usage by wave. Dark = confirmed used; light = unknown/null. TP3 is Emad/Ghadr-dominated; TP4 is Shahed-136-dominated.],
