== Systems Lost with IRIS Shahid Bagheri

Iran's drone carrier was struck and sunk by US forces on TP4's first day. It carried:
- Ababil-3N carrier drones
- Mohajer-6 armed UCAVs
- JAS-313 stealth drones (Qaher-313 derivative)
- Homa VTOL drones

These were destroyed before deployment.

